          "type": "FragmentSelector",
          "conformsTo": "http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/",
          "value": "xywh=pixel:1325.5556640625002,1530.963134765625,2757.586669921876,910.72265625"
        }
      },
      "@context": "http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld",
      "type": "Annotation",
      "body": [
        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "transcribing",
          "value": "PRAISED ARE YOU, Adonai our God, Ruler of the Universe,\nwho hallows us with mitzvot,\ncommanding us how to recite the Sh'ma:\nto declare wholeheartedly God's rule,\nto declare earnestly God is One,\nand to willingly worship God."
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-07-11T20:05:04.758Z",
      "creator": {
        "isGuest": true,
        "id": "2vi94ExIjdtwM7ddi4wa"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "80bda7ae-238a-4a67-8a2c-3dabd6e53342",
      "target": {
        "source": "mishkan:page:051c3a8f-0c58-444d-ada6-1a4ea721005d",
        "type": "SpecificResource",
        "selector": {
          "type": "FragmentSelector",
          "conformsTo": "http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/",
          "value": "xywh=pixel:1276.4907226562502,2879.3225097656255,2307.82470703125,1281.8115234374995"
        }
      },
      "@context": "http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld",
      "type": "Annotation",
      "body": [
        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "transcribing",
          "value": "THREE THINGS there are together in my eye\nthat keep the thought of Thee forever nigh.\nI think about Thy great and holy name\nwhenever I look up and see the sky.\nMy thoughts are roused to know how I was made,\nseeing the earth's expanse where I abide.\nThe musings of my mind when I look inside\nat all times, O my soul, \"Bless Adonai!\""
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-07-11T20:05:25.594Z",
      "creator": {
        "isGuest": true,
        "id": "2vi94ExIjdtwM7ddi4wa"
      }
    },
    {
